value.value: any structural anomaly of the anterior facial part of the face or muzzle containing the oral and nasal regions

definition.value: The term muzzle has multiple meanings and can be ambiguous. It has been added as a broad synonym, and in this case, refers both to the protruding part of the face seen in many animal species.
